7 sprzeda\u017c. Po tym okresie mo\u017cesz rozwa\u017cy\u0107 przej\u015bcie do drugiej struktury, aby uzyska\u0107 szerszy obraz wydajno\u015bci kampanii.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Wyb\u00f3r odpowiedniej struktury kampanii PPC jest kluczowy dla sukcesu na Amazonie. Pami\u0119taj, \u017ce ka\u017cdy produkt i rynek s\u0105 inne, dlatego warto testowa\u0107 r\u00f3\u017cne podej\u015bcia, aby znale\u017a\u0107 to, kt\u00f3re najlepiej odpowiada Twoim potrzebom. Podziel si\u0119 swoimi do\u015bwiadczeniami w komentarzach i napisz, jakie s\u0105 Twoje ulubione strategie!<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Jak zbudowa\u0107 skuteczn\u0105 kampani\u0119 PPC na Amazonie dla wi\u0119kszych katalog\u00f3w?<\/h2>\n<p>Jakie s\u0105 najle<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5052,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[2],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-5051","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kontent"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5051"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5051"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5051\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/5052"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5051"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/